					Remote work offers flexibility but requires clear communication.
					Remote work offers flexibility but requires clear communication.
					Remote work offers flexibility but requires clear communication.
					----------', messageType=SYSTEM, metadata={messageType=SYSTEM}
				},

				UserMessage{content='how are you', metadata={messageType=USER}, messageType=USER}
			],
